(It's) no wonder = it's not surpising 놀랍지도 않다.
What's the matter? = What's wrong? 뭐가 문제야?
have a stomachache = feel pain in one's stomach 배가아프다.
run a fever = have a high body temperature 고열이 나다.
That takes the cake! = That's really stange! That's the worst! 이거 진짜 이상하다!
make a mistake = do something incorrectly 실수하다.
get rid of something =  remove something 제거하다.
have cold feet = be afraid to do something 두려워하다.
put something off = delay or postpone something 연기하다, 미루다.
right away =  immediately 즉시, 바로